title: Sloppy Steaks @ Trendfoni's 8/26: Kristen Stewart, Kabul Airport, Jake Paul, California Recall, Premier League, Ron Jeremy

description:
In this edition of Sloppy Steaks @ Trendfoni's, Jack and Miles discuss Kristen Stewart being cast as Princess Diana, the suicide bombing at Kabul Airport, Jake Paul's upcoming MMA match, the California gubernatorial recall election, the massive transfers in the Premier League, and Ron Jeremy being indicted on over 30 counts of sexual assaults
